{"tid":218133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律巴打入]朋友屋企人想離婚，分身家問題","createTime":"2017-04-26T09:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T10:35:55.000Z","uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2335483091424379221eb985265f7f3e338d2b42","tid":218133,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"朋友22歲女仔，大學畢業做緊嘢<br />\n<br />\n佢父母不嬲關係好差，佢老豆見佢都大個做緊嘢就諗住離婚，我朋友就會跟老豆住<br />\n咁多年都係佢老豆養晒頭家，揾得唔多但係俾晒屋企，佢媽就從來無做過嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋有層樓就供甩，首期同供樓都係100%老豆出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問如果離婚有無機會可以留到層樓唔洗分?<br />\n同埋贍養費會點計?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1c3a459f79a062d14e91d91367df036519882a","tid":218133,"uid":73596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"你朋友就是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79f574554d68bdb020ba9ff8ebb5c06e025dbc0","tid":218133,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你朋友就是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82db5a1eef12b8e91b8e025845e54e4d294ca72e","tid":218133,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"層樓多數要分"},{"pid":"54e3b94e50d66e1bd195e088683ce2dbe40bebd5","tid":218133,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>層樓多數要分</blockquote><br />\n如果轉做個女個名呢?"},{"pid":"408c1063d0596e8806be0a6d55799607107fb606","tid":218133,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac8658ee37273740a4b46dd15bf66e9c5565799","tid":218133,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"女人唔做野都又想分人層樓，都幾大貪"},{"pid":"35ab6efaa40f466681001cd835c011456a60135d","tid":218133,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3fa33e65d340c29fedadcafc3d41c4cddd5af7","tid":218133,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"分一半外加每月固定贍養費"},{"pid":"9c670506a3da61a51f36515cccfc280ac58b467a","tid":218133,"uid":1083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分一半外加每月固定贍養費</blockquote><br />\n有無可能轉咗層樓俾個女，剩係俾贍養費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a70b7bd1b25b5dc7e3eae068093f7bed136ecec","tid":218133,"uid":30142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分一半外加每月固定贍養費</blockquote><br />\n有無可能轉咗層樓俾個女，剩係俾贍養費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定唔撚得, 轉名有個期限可以追訴,至於幾耐就唔記得,<br />\n等得就等個期限過左先離婚,<br />\n至於現金問題就比較易搞,<br />\n可以叫你老竇將可動用現金買曬儲蓄保,<br />\n唔好處係益左班保險佬, 但就唔使分現金身家只俾膽養費<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 幾年前有個FD離婚,幫佢問過班保險佬點樣可以只畀膽養費唔使分現金身家"},{"pid":"82209b0946ac7ef385b2cce31f897047b8357d34","tid":218133,"uid":53579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:39:08.000Z","msg":"一般而言<br />\n除非法院相信有特別情況<br />\n否則雙方的資產係需要平分"},{"pid":"b9cc60051c0e3f2f4d0640f31973b2c4a27ee33f","tid":218133,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分一半外加每月固定贍養費</blockquote><br />\n子女成咗年仲要俾？"},{"pid":"938963e532d202e5b6e95389723cc8c5833feb5f","tid":218133,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友22歲女仔，大學畢業做緊嘢<br />\n<br />\n佢父母不嬲關係好差，佢老豆見佢都大個做緊嘢就諗住離婚，我朋友就會跟老豆住<br />\n咁多年都係佢老豆養晒頭家，揾得唔多但係俾晒屋企，佢媽就從來無做過嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋有層樓就供甩，首期同供樓都係100%老豆出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問如果離婚有無機會可以留到層樓唔洗分?<br />\n同埋贍養費會點計?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n層樓寫邊個名先"},{"pid":"460e1c0d8a2f1da656c11c16815b3e745f2633b0","tid":218133,"uid":49015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"條女一世人離幾次婚 咁可以收幾多份善養費同身家？"},{"pid":"c314ad4bf33a81d9ae5f0fe0040994da4eb961b9","tid":218133,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分一半外加每月固定贍養費</blockquote><br />\n子女成咗年仲要俾？</blockquote><br />\n個老婆無做嘢，男嘅養開佢，就一定要"},{"pid":"feee5691e46c0e31f3dea421edd6e9ea83c0d455","tid":218133,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"做女人都幾著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525a9fa11892e41a76ac408f9042613d2b12f26d","tid":218133,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做女人都幾著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有閪真係大撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人死做爛做養個懶閪，個懶閪乜都唔做離婚就可以分個男人一半身家<br />\n公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2db6f9d85749fd8d64acc483c6df1c3fe1f095","tid":218133,"uid":20857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友22歲女仔，大學畢業做緊嘢<br />\n<br />\n佢父母不嬲關係好差，佢老豆見佢都大個做緊嘢就諗住離婚，我朋友就會跟老豆住<br />\n咁多年都係佢老豆養晒頭家，揾得唔多但係俾晒屋企，佢媽就從來無做過嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋有層樓就供甩，首期同供樓都係100%老豆出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問如果離婚有無機會可以留到層樓唔洗分?<br />\n同埋贍養費會點計?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先，婚姻長短好重要。如果係一段長嘅婚姻，就算首期同供樓係你爸爸出晒都冇用，因為法律上會假定有個common intention trust，層樓會被假定為婚姻資產（相關嘅考慮因素可以睇s7 MPPO）。係呢個情況下，法庭會以50/50作為基礎，去判定所有婚姻資產總和嘅分配。以上假設為雙方以一刀兩斷嘅形式去解除婚姻，如果任何一方傾向膽養費形式嘅附屬濟助，以上假設為未必適用。<br />\n<br />\n利申：PCLL，最好搵律師問。"},{"pid":"b95d9d7652197d36295b7137b79423efc1ab1cb0","tid":218133,"uid":55573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"其實最簡單就係叫個女方放棄層樓。"},{"pid":"32b873ba1b2dbf522cda33012ccff8cd032a604f","tid":218133,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你朋友就是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬73歲，所以朋友個老豆先係佢"}]}